#settingsPanel

	span.fa.fa-close#closeSettings

	.settingsWrap
		h3 스토리 모드
		hr
		p 스토리 모드를 사용하면 호출 프로세스를 단계별로 살펴볼 수 있습니다.
		p 처음 사용하는 경우 스토리 모드를 활성화하십시오. 

		br
		br
		p 
			span Story mode is 
			span#storyStatus.storyOn on
		p
			button(type="button")#disableStoryMode 비활성화
			span &nbsp;&nbsp;
			button(type="button" disabled="disabled")#enableStoryMode 활성화
	
	.settingsWrap(hidden)
		h3 
			span Endorsements
			span#construction (work in progress... does not work yet)
		hr
		p 
			span Proposals must be endorsed by a number of peers to be successful. 
			span The exact number of endorsements will be dictated by your network's policy. 
			span If you are new to Marbles or Fabric then select the first endorser. 
		br
		br
		p Every checked endorser below will receive marble proposals.
		
		.settingPeersWrap
			p 
				span Endorser 1
				input(type="text" placeholder="Peer URL" name="peer1").longer
				input(type="checkbox" name="peer1")

			p 
				span Endorser 2
				input(type="text" placeholder="Peer URL" name="peer2").longer
				input(type="checkbox" name="peer2")

		p
			button(type="button" disabled="disabled") Add Endorser

	